TY  - JOUR
AB  - The two factors, the rate base and the rate of return. The rules governing the court and commission decisions in valuation cases, 606.--Mostly questions of opinion, 607.--Ambiguity of the term "value." "Investment" a better word for the purpose, 608.--Suggestion for handling appreciation as income, 610.-- Consideration of the rate of return. Three criteria proposed, 612.--Too much dependence on "judicial notice." Other delicate problems, 612.--A summary, 613.
